{"tid":2391757,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何柱國賣星島 28% 股權　佳兆業太子女郭曉亭接貨","createTime":"2021-02-02T11:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T11:46:21.000Z","uid":390066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64fc0c72314ceba50203bf1d53ddd9202cf5f584","tid":2391757,"uid":390066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"何柱國賣星島 28% 股權 佳兆業太子女郭曉亭接貨<br />\n立場報道2021/2/2 &mdash; 17:41<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4BRqDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4BRqDv.png&h=dbfb3b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星島新聞集團 （1105）賣盤有新進展。聯交所股權披露顯示，星島集團主席兼大股東何柱國上周四在場外以現金每股 1.5 元，沽售手上星島 28 %股權，套現近 3.7 億元，股份買家是佳兆業「太子女」、年僅 27 歲的郭曉亭。<br />\n<br />\n星島上周五停牌，以待公布內幕消息，但今日（2日）暫未有公布。星島集團停牌前報 0.91 元，以場外價每股 1.5 元計，今次股份交易的溢價約 65%。<br />\n<br />\n聯交所股權披露權益顯示，星島（1105）主席主席兼大股東何柱國，已於1月28日訂立股份出售協議，申報在場外，已每股現金外價 1.5元，沽售手上星島集團共 28% 股權，即 2.46 億股，套現逾 3.69億元。<br />\n股權披露顯示，何柱國仍保留 3.37% 星島股權。內房股佳兆業（1638）主席郭英成的女兒郭曉亭，同日申報，在場外以每股 1.5元，購入該批股份。<br />\n<br />\n星島新聞集團由全國政協何柱國任主席，立場被視為親政府，經營報章包括《星島日報》、《頭條日報》、《 The Standard》、另經營《東周刊》、《 Jet》等雜誌。集團去年底傳出賣盤，但一直未公布最終協定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/何柱國賣星島-28-股權-佳兆業太子女郭曉亭接貨/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E4%BD%95%E6%9F%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%A3%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-28-%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A-%E4%BD%B3%E5%85%86%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%AD%E6%9B%89%E4%BA%AD%E6%8E%A5%E8%B2%A8%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BFScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=1a89fd48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E4%BD%95%E6%9F%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%A3%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-28-%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A-%E4%BD%B3%E5%85%86%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%AD%E6%9B%89%E4%BA%AD%E6%8E%A5%E8%B2%A8%2F&h=014a7bd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/何柱國賣星島-28-股權-佳兆業太子女郭曉亭接貨/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反拉反拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢條友 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛國愛黨<br />\n黨安法咁穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都要撤資<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時d愛國情懷去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係政協 又乜乜柒柒"},{"pid":"9a2b887b259f63368667bfcca765379278e3af2e","tid":2391757,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf57d17d6c5b56121182f3079dc60a1653e3313","tid":2391757,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"走佬LU&nbsp;走得慢渣都無"},{"pid":"695233d42c4ceeba58a530a5e38b64df7d024efe","tid":2391757,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"咪撚畀依條撚樣走呀"}]}